headline: Fifth Third Recognized on Forbes List of the World’s Best Banks 2025
summary: CINCINNATI, April 10, 2025--Fifth Third (Nasdaq: FITB) has been recognized as one of the World’s Best Banks 2025 by Forbes and Statista Inc. The ranking recognizes the best banks in 34 countries based on an independent survey sample of more than 50,000 consumers.
